Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:59.01,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}バニラソルトで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:00.89,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Burning Love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:08.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}アマいだけなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:13.59,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ソルトかけましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:20.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰よりももっともっと私を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:23.49,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}知って欲しいからさらけだしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:26.97,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}でも出来ないの　経験Nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:28.75,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}モドカシすぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:35.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}でも、アマいだけの愛はちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:43.49,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}私が求めているモノとは違う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:47.09,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}シロと言われたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:50.57,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}クロだって言っちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:54.03,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}素直になれない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:56.42,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}アマノジャク
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:23:00.85,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}スキと言われたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.05,0:23:04.34,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ダイキライだって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:10.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嬉しいのにナニ言ってんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:17.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}アマいバニラに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:22.01,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ソルトかけるよに…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:59.01,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}香草加上鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:00.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}燃燒的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:08.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}太過甜蜜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:13.59,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就撒上鹽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:20.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想你比誰都更多更多地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:23.49,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}瞭解我  因此想表現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:26.97,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是卻做不到  經驗為零
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:28.75,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}太令人著急
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:35.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是只有甜蜜的愛的話卻有點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:43.49,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}和我所希望的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:50.57,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被說成是白的話  卻偏要說是黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:56.42,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無法變誠實的  鬧彆扭的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:23:04.34,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被你說喜歡  卻要說討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:10.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明明高興  卻是口不對心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:17.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}猶如甜蜜的香草
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:22.01,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}撒上鹽一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------正文------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都說到這個份上了就和你結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}高須龍兒的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龍看呀看呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河妹妹她生下了這麼多小寶寶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.90,0:00:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}實錄恐怖列島日本～我生下了狗的小寶寶～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為借了無聊的DVD害我做了這種夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是夢這也太糟糕了  那樣的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  大河
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了個好討厭的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.63,0:00:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是狗  狗是我的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:00:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕透頂的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預警夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果沒有什麼對策的話就會有那樣\N悲慘的未來在等著你喲」的警告啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夢是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  為了改變未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想明天開始的旅行有一方要全力地支援另一方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我倒是明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥是羽毛球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所·以·說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是要來決定麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個「有一方」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好  無論如何都不要用明火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米糠一天攪拌一次  小鸚的水早晚都要換
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的都寫下來了去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出門…去哪裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過了  去旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了泰泰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天會是好天氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託了哦  那個「作戰」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你贏好了  快點把這傢伙拿開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有那只笨狗亂入的話就是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你想用自己的得意項目來決勝負才會遭報應的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  扯上狗的事都沒有好下場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  真的能順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.73,0:04:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次旅行結束的時候  你和小實之間就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  你們兩個時間都剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起  了不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦  沒精神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來說句話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是最棒的出遊日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來亞美還沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離集合時間還差一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都沒來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲…喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到了兩分鐘哦  亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  亞～美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢死了啦  笨蛋吉娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大家在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別逃啊笨蛋吉娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞美  我們在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃啊這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了梅子超好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}註：日語裏「梅子」和「好吃」諧音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是高須呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要嫁到我家來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  逢阪好像還沒來難道遲到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須有聯絡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  笨蛋吉醒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你睜著眼睛睡著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去旅行就別吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  川島在暑假都在做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？  一直在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又開始工作了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}社團打工社團打工社團社團打工社團打工社團打工社團…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大河呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了大河
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才好像聽到「前輩」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣奇怪的聲音  這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  從預約附贈CD裏收集的靈異聲音集
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  我被叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢阪喜歡這樣恐怖的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛枝會害怕靈異相關的東西倒也讓人覺得意外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕害怕超害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是超害怕應該是非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小實說她對恐怖  靈異  所有超自然現象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的都很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我和你來讓小實害怕得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  墮入恐怖的絕望中的小實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由你去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「櫛枝由我來保護」…這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,題目就是「讓小實害怕  騎士登場作戰」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  可怕的事情絕對禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  要走到哪裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉到裏面去  這樣的話就可以上到台階去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是亞美的別墅？  要在這住下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  小實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害  超感激
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  先得從打掃開始才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年起就沒人來過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去…去年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這好像還真是場艱苦的戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼美麗的大海就在眼前哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃什麼的待會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  打掃就等會兒再做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去了  高須同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會一個人在打掃啊  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  看起來是不是像個人頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  淹死的屍體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  我被泡在屍水裏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很高興的樣子呢  那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的來了呢  佑作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這當然要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須都來了  作為好友的我怎麼可以不來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會那裏沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞美叫我們去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倉庫裏面好像有機車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機車？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就帶大河去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢阪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不去  我害怕機車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得有兩人獨處的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有我的想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在兩人回來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到能實行「那個作戰」的地點才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是害羞的話就坦率…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蚊子啊  蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  就算說能實行的地方也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…洗手間麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也要打掃才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我沒發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現…現在就出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大膽呢  竟然在女孩子淋浴的時候進來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…又不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦  現在的話可以和大家保密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  不想做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做…做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  你到底在期待什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊這個表情  真是傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋吉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝成在淋浴的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩弄了男生的純情？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  二樓的調查完成了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窩囊廢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣你才會被笨蛋吉玩弄的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便向笨蛋吉抱怨一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  笨蛋吉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋吉真的在洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋吉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啵」的「啵」的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「彭--」的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說些多餘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北村呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是去停車了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛枝都已經把東西買來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有什麼東西碰到了我的…我的脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛…剛才的確被什麼東西碰到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘糊糊的  好像是海藻之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是海藻的氣味  是海藻啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被海藻纏死的動物的幽靈一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海獺  說到海藻的話就是海獺的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮口袋裏裝滿扇貝屍體的海獺的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是海獺和海藻的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我不要辣味的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡辣味的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是甜的要怎麼吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  龍兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦  之後會單為你做份甜味的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又只對逢阪特別對待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會被女孩子討厭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小實也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快完成了嗎  做得真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差放咖喱塊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  你們也去準備吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經準備晚飯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙擺盤子什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大河
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑作  你還正常嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聽到高須的聲音了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來還有女生在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:12:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻不傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河  振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這天賜的自戀少年  快露出裸體來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}註：Narcissus，希臘神話裏戀上自己的倒影，最後變成水僊的自戀少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣子你還說什麼呀  你這裝模做樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有黑黑的…毛茸茸的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是海藻的幽靈吧  大概
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海…藻…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛枝？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑作…太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  你快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個屋子裏瀰漫著邪惡的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼  我能做到的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把咖喱…做得超級辣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是臨時拼湊的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也按照櫛枝的要求盡量做得辣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  要吃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不錯不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒有預想的辣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.84,0:14:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大河也嘗嘗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  不怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小實？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這在喉嚨裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說辣又好像是…燙…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了  衝到頭上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇塞  又來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超辣超美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此  不可思議後勁很大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像感覺很奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有的添哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  那我去洗餐具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吃得太辣了  我想吃胃藥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子痛嗎  藥好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢阪  不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胃藥的話我帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在房間裏  要一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…等…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兩個人獨處的機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞美美也肚子痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  因為看你在發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著你真是不會厭倦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在誇我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很微妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛那是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  可以的話現在一起去海邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂高須同學  幫忙拿一下那邊的玻璃杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  說什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  管用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…概
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著好像很難受的逢阪  我也會很難過的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  難受的話要躺一會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你洗東西的技術還真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為打工時幹了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須才是  那真是技術高超的咖喱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為幫忙的謝禮給你個好東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對大家要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹茶好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:16:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口味還一般般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多星星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很…很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛…櫛枝  有…有男朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才海藻的幽靈還在這附近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須  看見過幽靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒看見過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著這個世界上有幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也沒真的見過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一點也不相信那些見過的人所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且呢  同樣地也想過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也相信將來有一天會戀愛會結婚變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是實際卻沒有對誰有過這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上那些理所當然地談著戀愛的人  對我來說非常遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我看不見嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不存在幽靈  一生也不會見到了  都快要放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以對你的問題的回答是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須同學呢  你能看得見幽靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概是想看見的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也會去神秘現象多發地點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會看恐怖片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有靈感的人第一次看到幽靈的時候也會吃驚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看到了  但想著「果然是不存在」而打消念頭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反也許也有經過努力才終於看見的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你也不用就認定了「一生都不可能見到」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UFO？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造衛星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造衛星…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  還以為是UFO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得櫛枝也什麼時候能見到幽靈就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定也有想被你看到的幽靈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天總是發生奇怪的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在向我強調自己的存在呀  海藻的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼呀  這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候能看見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒  我的肚子好像不痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  明天怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是說那個作戰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全沒有在好好幹呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這回是負責支援的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  話說回來還真是累
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為一整天都能和北村同學在一起是多麼幸福的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是緊張過頭  好像都要折壽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在一起明明一點都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊  真失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傻呢  明明是這麼寬敞的屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還這樣粘著坐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是習慣狹小的公寓了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有時在想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夢…  意外地…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我有把包在這裏放過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好像還粘糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為這個是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明放在包裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才摸了一下還是暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像誰剛才還穿著似的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的房間也很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枕頭上有長長的頭髮…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…剛才的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不  一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這一定是夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒錯  是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個變成狗住在狗屋的夢的後續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…閉上眼到時就會醒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會醒的會醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕好可怕好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖好可怕幽靈好可怕魔獸好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點  櫛枝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最可怕的大概是UFO

